00:16:45.159 --> 00:16:47.119
it, it cuts across all these domains.

293
00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:50.500
Mhm. And what would you say are the main

294
00:16:50.500 --> 00:16:53.979
challenges of developing a science of virtue?

295
00:16:55.369 --> 00:16:57.789
The biggest challenge, the one that we're struggling with

296
00:16:57.789 --> 00:17:02.030
now is measurement, um, because the vast majority of

