00:17:02.030 --> 00:17:09.868
virtue science is done with self-report scales. Um, SO

298
00:17:09.868 --> 00:17:12.150
I, you know, if you were one of my

299
00:17:12.150 --> 00:17:15.868
participants, I would give you a measure of virtue,

300
00:17:16.348 --> 00:17:19.670
some virtue or another, and ask you how well

301
00:17:19.670 --> 00:17:21.709
you think you do it. Well, that has some

302
00:17:21.709 --> 00:17:25.199
obvious problems in that. Uh, ONE, you might want

303
00:17:25.199 --> 00:17:28.300
to deceive me. That's the most obvious, um, and

304
00:17:28.300 --> 00:17:30.109
that's the one psychologists spent a lot of time

305
00:17:30.109 --> 00:17:33.119
on, but also, you might be more or less

306
00:17:33.119 --> 00:17:38.349
self-aware. So you might not even know that, um,

307
00:17:38.979 --> 00:17:43.140
let's say, uh, you have a a cruel streak

