00:19:45.140 --> 00:19:48.380
valid because people are willing to say in the

344
00:19:48.380 --> 00:19:52.660
last 2 hours I was dishonest with someone, or

345
00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:58.010
in the last 2 hours I acted quite fairly

346
00:19:58.010 --> 00:20:00.380
and they're much more willing to admit faults and

347
00:20:00.380 --> 00:20:02.939
weaknesses for a short period of time than they

348
00:20:02.939 --> 00:20:06.339
are to say, oh, in general I'm a dishonest

349
00:20:06.339 --> 00:20:10.750
person, or in general I'm a cruel person. Um,

350
00:20:13.020 --> 00:20:15.160
So that's another way to do it. And there

351
00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:16.880
are a variety of ways to get around these

352
00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:19.599
challenges, but I think, uh, we need to, we

353
00:20:19.599 --> 00:20:21.839
need to work on it. So virtue science right

354
00:20:21.839 --> 00:20:26.180
now is, um, In its infancy, it's only been

