00:22:06.380 --> 00:22:11.900
early questions, but what does virtue mean exactly? For

386
00:22:11.900 --> 00:22:17.209
instance, does it vary cross culturally? And if so,

387
00:22:17.459 --> 00:22:21.170
does that then imply that we should be committed

